name: Eva Air 747-45E [B-16411] Dusk Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
One of my favorite videos from this trip! Here we have Eva Air flight 10 landing at Vancouver International Airport from Taipei, with a spectacular backdrop in the form of Mount Baker. ATC is included, enjoy this sunset arrival!

Thanks for watching!
